overview: While having lunch on a distant roadside, Dovydas sees an extravagantly dressed girl Aiste, wandering in the horizon. He agrees to give her a ride to the nearest café, where Aiste rushes to see a video report about herself on TV. Step by step, Dovydas starts to suspect that Aiste has created a fictional version of herself, and tension between them raises a question: are they really just strangers to one another?

production_companies.name: Lithuanian Academy of Music and Theatre

title: Time Will Come
